{"_id":"EWoyR4JKrpIdO02p","name":"Bell - The Speaker","type":"misc","img":"modules/morkborg-3p/images/tokens/the-bellfounder.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-size: 13px;\">1. Those who hear the bell's toll are compelled to tell the truth.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-size: 13px;\">2. The bell's ring causes creatures to speak in tongues, allowing cretures to understand one another.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-size: 13px;\">3. Anyone who hears the bell cannot speak for d4 minutes.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-size: 13px;\">4. The bell resonates with the dead, allowing them to speak.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"EI4zbOlxQspAyGze":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.r7fPJhnF0DqEdo8x"}}}
{"_id":"JNvP1NLKQ577RBQw","name":"\"The\" Bellfounder","type":"class","img":"modules/morkborg-3p/images/tokens/the-bellfounder.png","data":{"abilities":"<p>The dying world resonates to the sound of your bells, roll 3d6+2 for Presence. Your craft is cast in the forge, you have little use the fast and impatient, roll 3d6-2 for Agility. You forged your weapon, although perhaps not as expertly as your bells, roll d6 for weapons and d2 for armor.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Cost for mundane bell founding:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Small Bell (Ornamental, Service) 10s</li>\n<li>Medium Bell (Hand) 20s</li>\n<li>Large Bell (Farm) 40s</li>\n<li>Behemoth Bell (Church) 80s</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","armorTableDie":"1d2","description":"You have heard the death knell of the world. The foundry was your escape, until you found the Bells. Their resonance has the power to change everything. You know it. Even the power to change you...","omenDie":"1d2","startingAgility":"3d6-2","startingHitPoints":"1d4","startingItems":"morkborg-3p.class-the-bellfounder,Bell Ringer","startingPresence":"3d6+2","startingRolls":"morkborg-3p.rolls-the-bellfounder,First Bell,1\nmorkborg-3p.rolls-the-bellfounder,For Whom Does the Bell Toll?,1","startingSilver":"1d6*10","startingStrength":"3d6","startingToughness":"3d6","weaponTableDie":"1d6"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"EI4zbOlxQspAyGze":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.xfZSbgcyi2hFw1lK"}}}
{"_id":"U8LLbrA0DnDyjMTR","name":"Bell - The Thinker","type":"misc","img":"modules/morkborg-3p/images/tokens/the-bellfounder.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>1. Any forgotten or surpressed memories return to those who hear the bell's toll.</p>\n<p>2. The bell's toll returns to a dead creature its' soul, personality, and independent thought.</p>\n<p>3. The sound of the bell wipes all memory from those who hear it for d4 hours.</p>\n<p>4. A creature's soul, personality, and independent thought are torn from them, leaving a mindless servant.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"EI4zbOlxQspAyGze":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.2mdLtG25UD8KCifP"}}}
{"_id":"eTRIlfCuvHUc1Rvw","name":"Bell - The Sleeper","type":"misc","img":"modules/morkborg-3p/images/tokens/the-bellfounder.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>1. The ringer is shrouded in silence making them aurally undetectable for d4 minutes.</p>\n<p>2. The bell casts the area into haunting silence for d4 turns.</p>\n<p>3. Everyone who hears the bell must make a DR14 Presence Test or fall asleep for d4 turns.</p>\n<p>4. All creatures who hear the bell's ring fall into a deep slumber for d4 hours.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"EI4zbOlxQspAyGze":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.dlzTK89z9Xlc9K6G"}}}
{"_id":"j7wKqQIinR5wFo8p","name":"Bell - The Binder","type":"misc","img":"modules/morkborg-3p/images/tokens/the-bellfounder.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>1. Shackles all undead within the bell's range to the ringer's will.</p>\n<p>2. Those who hear the bell are forced to stop, bound in time, for d4 turns.</p>\n<p>3. A creature who hears the bell's toll is compelled to follow a command from the ringer.</p>\n<p>4. One creature within ear shot of the bell's ring must follow commands form the ringer for d4 hours.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"EI4zbOlxQspAyGze":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.xRR2HSnbXP8CNA66"}}}
{"_id":"m37u92PSujIAPUJC","name":"Bell - The Walker","type":"misc","img":"modules/morkborg-3p/images/tokens/the-bellfounder.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-size: 13px;\">1. At the bell's toll, pass into ethereal space, reentering perceived reality next turn.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-size: 13px;\">2. The bell's ring allows another creature to take an additional turn.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-size: 13px;\">3. The sound of the bell compels all creatures who hear it to flee.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-size: 13px;\">4. All craetures who hear the toll of the bell are paralyzed for d4 turns.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"EI4zbOlxQspAyGze":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.a1nNP4pcgnKBpkmI"}}}
{"_id":"zPWUaDDsT5Xv1GTX","name":"Bell - The Waker","type":"misc","img":"modules/morkborg-3p/images/tokens/the-bellfounder.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>1. Anyone who hears the bells toll awakens from any delusions they suffer from.</p>\n<p>2. Everyone within the bell's range wakes from sleep or unconciousness.</p>\n<p>3. As the bell tolls, a dead creature wakes from the eternal slumber of death as a zombie or skeleton.</p>\n<p>4. All creature who hear the bell's ring awaken the slumber of death as zombies or skeletons.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"EI4zbOlxQspAyGze":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Q1EdfU5qCcV7Mn90"}}}
